Swagger in Magento 

Magento 2 REST API is based on openAI specification (OAS) or Swagger Specifications, OAS are meant for how we can describe, structure and 
visualize api resources. 

Magento 2 RESTFUl API swagger is based on swagger specification and uses Swagger UI tool to generate and visualize API documentation so it
can be easily unerstood and used. 

Magento2 provides Magento_Swagger module to list, visualize and at the same time test API resources.


==> http://website-base-url/swagger
